      <title>利比亚央行僵局加剧，行长不愿让步</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/libyan-central-bank-standoff-deepens-as-governor-won-t-back-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[陷入困境的利比亚央行行长坚持抵制罢免他的企图，这加深了敌对派系之间为争夺这个四分五裂的欧佩克国家巨额石油收入控制权而持续一周多的僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/libyan-central-bank-standoff-deepens-as-governor-won-t-back-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 15:12:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京会见指挥官，泽连斯基谈及“公平和平”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-wants-kursk-incursion-to-nudge-russia-toward-peace</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总统泽连斯基表示，乌克兰在俄罗斯库尔斯克地区的行动是更广泛的军事、政治和外交努力的一部分，旨在让俄罗斯接受“公平的和平”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/war-in-ukraine-zelenskiy-wants-kursk-incursion-to-nudge-russia-toward-peace</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 12:39:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯通过大会捐款突破 5 亿美元大关</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/harris-crosses-half-billion-donation-milestone-with-convention</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选团队及其附属机构在上周芝加哥举行的民主党全国代表大会上筹集了 8200 万美元，自总统乔·拜登宣布卸任以来，他们的总筹款额已达到 5.4 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/harris-crosses-half-billion-donation-milestone-with-convention</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 25 Aug 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
