      <title>路透社记者在俄罗斯袭击克拉马托尔斯克事件中受伤</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-25/two-reuters-journalists-wounded-in-russian-strike-on-kramatorsk</link>
